Azure Spot Virtual Machines provide unused Azure capacity at discounted rates.

Benefits:

* Major cost savings
* Suitable for interruptible workloads

Limitations:

* Can be evicted when Azure needs capacity

For example, batch processing jobs or test workloads can use Spot VMs.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is ML model training experiments.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is rendering workloads.

Spot pricing is ideal for flexible, non-critical compute needs.
